OL,3,CPolice watchdog launches investigation
OL,4,Cinto Hampshire chief constable
OL,6,FThe chief constable of Hampshire
OL,7,FConstabulary is being investigated by
OL,8,Fthe police watchdog following an
OL,9,Fallegation surrounding a "previous
OL,10,Frelationship".
OL,12,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,13,FConduct (IOPC) confirmed it had
OL,14,Flaunched the probe into a claim made
OL,15,Fagainst Scott Chilton, who is also the
OL,16,Fnational lead for chief constables for
OL,17,Fboth investigations and tactics,
OL,18,Ftraining and equipment.
