OL,3,CPolice watchdog launches investigation
OL,4,Cinto Hampshire chief constable
OL,6,FAn IOPC spokeswoman said: "We have
OL,7,Fbegun an independent investigation
OL,8,Finto the conduct of the Hampshire and
OL,9,FIsle of Wight Constabulary's Chief
OL,10,FConstable Scott Chilton.
OL,12,F"The investigation involves
OL,13,Fallegations the chief constable failed
OL,14,Fto disclose a conflict of interest
OL,15,Frelating to a previous relationship.
OL,17,F"Our investigation began following a
OL,18,Freferral from the Hampshire Police and
OL,19,FCrime Commissioner on February 27 and
OL,20,Fis in its early stages."
