OL,3,CPolice watchdog launches investigation
OL,4,Cinto Hampshire chief constable
OL,6,FDonna Jones, police and crime
OL,7,Fcommissioner for Hampshire and the
OL,8,FIsle of Wight, said Mr Chilton would
OL,9,Fremain in post during the
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FShe said: "A historic report has led
OL,13,Fto a mandatory referral to the IOPC,
OL,14,Fas is normal procedure in these cases.
OL,16,F"The chief constable remains in post
OL,17,Fand has my full support to continue
OL,18,Freducing crime, increasing detection
OL,19,Frates and making communities safer
OL,20,Facross Hampshire and the Isle of
OL,21,FWight."
