OL,3,CPolice watchdog launches investigation
OL,4,Cinto Hampshire chief constable
OL,6,FAccording to the Hampshire
OL,7,FConstabulary website, Mr Chilton was
OL,8,Fappointed chief constable of the force
OL,9,Fin February 2023.
OL,11,FIt states: "This is Mr Chilton's
OL,12,Fsecond spell with Hampshire after
OL,13,Fjoining in 1992.
OL,15,F"He initially worked his way through
OL,16,Funiformed policing before joining the
OL,17,Fcriminal investigations department
OL,18,F(CID) in 1996, spending the next 16
OL,19,Fyears as a detective.
