OL,3,CPolice watchdog launches investigation
OL,4,Cinto Hampshire chief constable
OL,6,F"Mr Chilton progressed to the rank of
OL,7,Fchief superintendent, overseeing many
OL,8,Fcomplex major crime investigations.
OL,10,F"Mr Chilton is now the national lead,
OL,11,Fon behalf of all chief constables, for
OL,12,Finvestigations ` which includes
OL,13,Fstandards and accreditation, retention
OL,14,Fand recruitment of detectives,
OL,15,Fhomicide and coronial investigations.
OL,17,F"He is also the chief constable lead
OL,18,Ffor tactics, training and equipment in
OL,19,Fthe public order and public safety
OL,20,Fenvironment."
